***DISPLAYING THE AGE OF THE PERSON IN DESCENDING ORDER(ELDEST FIRST)***


--->CODE

names=["Diya","Sana","Hemanth","Cleo"]
age=[12,67,36,34]
res=list(zip(age,names))
res1=sorted(res,reverse=True)
p=1
for i in res1:
    print("{}. {} age is {}".format(p, i[1],i[0]))
    p=p+1



~OUTPUT

1. Sana age is 67
2. Hemanth age is 36
3. Cleo age is 34
4. Diya age is 12
